{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389100/extras/logo2.png?t=1735415314\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389100/extras/RMIlI6.gif?t=1735415314\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Engine</u></strong>:  RPGMaker VX Ace</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Status</u></strong>: In-development</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Length</u></strong>: 5-6 hours\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Genre</u></strong>: Adventure, Fantasy, minor horror elements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389100/extras/story.png?t=1735415314\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the world of Arcadea, people can accomplish their dreams. How? Through video games of course! Everybody who lives in Arcadea has a special arcade machine they can visit in their dreams that lets them fulfill their strongest wishes. Whether it\u2019s to go on an adventure, or make friends, or fall in love, or solve a mystery, or completely start a new life, there\u2019s a game made just for them...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">By playing these arcade machines, you can find out a lot about a person\u2026their aspirations and their goals for example. Oh and also their regrets, their insecurities, and their biggest mistakes. Huh...video games can\u2019t be that deep right? Must be a bug or something.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speaking of which, how do you even get to this world in the first place? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game follows Maisie, a new arrival to Arcadea. She\u2019s not very interested in all this gaming stuff; her only goal is to find an important person. But along the way, she can\u2019t help but be roped into other people\u2019s problems. She also can\u2019t help that the arcade machines seem to glitch around her. Alot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389100/extras/features.png?t=1735415314\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mini-games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Custom Mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Original Art and Music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple Endings</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389100/extras/bird.gif?t=1735415314\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389100/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735415314","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389100/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1735415314","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389100/fdf9170bfc0a5becdd67e571b6b8dbff7a29a51c/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735415314","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389100/fdf9170bfc0a5becdd67e571b6b8dbff7a29a51c/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735415314","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3397250,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389100/extras/logo2.png?t=1735415314\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389100/extras/RMIlI6.gif?t=1735415314\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Engine</u></strong>:  RPGMaker VX Ace</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Status</u></strong>: In-development</